  "title": "Permanent Marketing Executive at Henderson Road, Up to $2,800 + Performance Incentives + Bonus (Office hours)",
  "description": "<p><strong>- Permanent</strong></p><p><strong>- Up to $2,800 + Performance Incentives + Bonus</strong></p><p><strong>- Mon to  Fri: 9am – 6pm</strong></p><p><strong>- Henderson Road</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><p><strong>Marketing & Lead Generation</strong></p><ul><li>Plan and execute<strong> social media marketing</strong> across:LinkedIn<br />TikTok<br />Facebook<br />Email marketing (EDM)<br /></li><li>Develop and schedule content / campaigns to promote corporate gifting services and new products</li><li>Support B2B branding initiatives across online touchpoints</li><li>Track and analyse marketing performance (engagement, conversion, lead quality)</li></ul><p><strong>Sales Support</strong></p><ul><li>Manage inbound leads from marketing channels</li><li>Call and arrange appointments with potential clients</li><li>Maintain customer database</li><li>Work with sales team to ensure smooth handover of qualified leads</li></ul><p><strong>General</strong></p><ul><li>Assist with product marketing activities</li><li>Support small ad-hoc projects & campaigns</li><li>Coordinate with internal teams on marketing materials</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Duration:</strong></p><ul><li>Permanent</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Location:</strong></p><ul><li>Henderson Road</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Working Hours:</strong></p><ul><li>Mon to  Fri: 9am – 6pm</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Salary:</strong></p><ul><li>Up to $2,800 + Performance Incentives + Bonus</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>1–2 years experience</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Interested applicants, kindly email your detailed resume (MS Word format is preferred):</p><p>​​​<strong>cass@successhrc.com.sg</strong> (Reg No: <strong>R2197670</strong>)</p><p><br /></p><p>Please ensure that applications sent through email are no bigger than 1Mb.</p><p>We thank all applicants for your interest but regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates would be notified.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Success Human Resource Centre Pte Ltd</strong> (EA License Number: <strong>97C4832</strong>)</p><p>160 Robinson Road, #13-07/08/09 SBF Center, Singapore 068914</p><p>T: 6337 3183 | W: <a href=\"http://www.successhrc.com.sg/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">www.successhrc.com.sg</a></p>",
